@startuml api_facade_state

[*] --> Idle

Idle --> ReceiveRequest : apiRequest()
ReceiveRequest --> ValidateRequest

ValidateRequest --> Error : invalid request
ValidateRequest --> AuthorizeRequest : valid request

AuthorizeRequest --> Error : unauthorized
AuthorizeRequest --> DispatchRequest : authorized

DispatchRequest --> FormatResponse : result received
DispatchRequest --> Error : processing failed

FormatResponse --> ReturnResponse
ReturnResponse --> Idle

Error --> Idle

@enduml